Black Asian Native American Department Figures 94% 6% 83.9% 9% 3.2% 1.9% 1.9% 
ACLU Figures 94% 6% 87.3% 8.6% 2.6% 0 * 
</P>
<P>
 Burbank Fire Department 07,20,06,08,07,08,07,07 Male Female White Latino Black 
Asian Department Figures 100% 0 89.2% 8.4% 0.7% 1.5% ACLU figures 100% 0 92.1% 
