<HEADLINE>
<P>
WOMAN, 42, DIES IN FAMILY POOL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 42-year-old Sherman Oaks woman drowned Sunday when she fell in the family 
pool, Los Angeles police said. 
</P>
<P>
 The woman was pronounced dead about 1:40 p.m. after falling in the pool in the 
5500 block of Leghorn Avenue, officers said. 
</P>
<P>
 Police said the drowning appears to be an accident. 
</P>
</TEXT>
